Package kalix.javasdk.testkit.junit.jupiter

  • Annotation Types Summary 
    Annotation Type Description
    KalixDescriptor
    The @KalixDescriptor annotation is used in conjunction with the KalixTest annotation to mark the Kalix that should be managed by the kalix Testkit extension.
    KalixTest
    @KalixTest registers a JUnit Jupiter extension to automatically manage the lifecycle of KalixTestKit.
